msgid ""
"Snapshots will be named <prefix>-YYYYMMDD-HHMMSS and stored in "
"<mountpoint>/.snapshots/<subvolume>/."
msgstr ""
"快照將被命名為 <prefix>-YYYYMMDD-HHMMSS 並儲存於 <mountpoint>/.snapshots/<subvolume>/。"

